00:32:24,810 --> 00:32:27,170
Leaving? Where are you going?

512
00:32:27,170 --> 00:32:30,509
I'm going to a wood carving workshop in Xiamen to improve my skills.

513
00:32:30,509 --> 00:32:31,969
Did you tell your master?

514
00:32:31,969 --> 00:32:34,319
Yes, I told him. He's supportive of me.

515
00:32:34,319 --> 00:32:36,660
Besides, I plan on coming back.

516
00:32:36,660 --> 00:32:38,610
Good for you.

517
00:32:39,350 --> 00:32:42,550
Such an abrupt piece of news makes me hesitant to let you go.

518
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:46,819
We always meet, but you're leaving for such a faraway place.

519
00:32:46,819 --> 00:32:48,650
Really?

520
00:32:50,970 --> 00:32:53,120
Will you reply to my text messages?

521
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:56,370
Of course, I will. Why would I ignore your messages?

522
00:32:57,730 --> 00:32:59,680
It's a promise then.

523
00:33:07,650 --> 00:33:13,680
Xia Xia... I've always treated you as a younger brother.

524
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:21,990
I know. It's okay.

525
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:27,640
Take good care of yourself when you're in Xiamen.

526
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:29,300
I will.

527
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:37,740
Whose cattle left so much dung here?

528
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:40,900
It must've been a herd of cattle.

529
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:48,070
I'm back again!

530
00:33:51,170 --> 00:33:54,660
It's still the same. Nothing has changed.

531
00:33:56,340 --> 00:33:59,639
Look. The futon you meditated on hasn't been worn out yet.

532
00:33:59,639 --> 00:34:03,559
Sorry. This is a private residence. Visitors aren't allowed to enter.

533
00:34:03,559 --> 00:34:07,649
Hello. We used to live here, so we're just stopping by.

534
00:34:07,649 --> 00:34:12,470
Gentlemen, this place isn't open to visitors and pictures aren't allowed.

535
00:34:12,470 --> 00:34:15,560
- Aunty A'Gui!
- Aunty A'Gui!

536
00:34:15,560 --> 00:34:19,710
Xiao Hu! Mr. Ma! How are you?

537
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:22,240
- I'm good.
- Excellent.

538
00:34:22,240 --> 00:34:23,739
I'm sorry about that.

539
00:34:23,739 --> 00:34:25,150
There are a lot more tourists in the village,

540
00:34:25,150 --> 00:34:27,670
and there are people trying to take photos all day long.

541
00:34:27,670 --> 00:34:29,500
Are you here to travel?

542
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:32,409
President Xu's homestay is having a soft opening.

543
00:34:32,409 --> 00:34:35,570
She reserved two rooms for us. So, we decided to take a vacation here this weekend.

544
00:34:35,570 --> 00:34:38,380
Wonderful!

545
00:34:38,380 --> 00:34:40,340
How has your work been?

546
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:42,210
Thanks to your blessings, I've been doing great.

547
00:34:42,210 --> 00:34:44,679
Me too. Sister Manjun is doing fabulously.

548
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:47,080
That's wonderful!

549
00:34:47,080 --> 00:34:48,350
What about you? How are you doing?

550
00:34:48,350 --> 00:34:50,050
Of course, I'm doing good.

551
00:34:50,050 --> 00:34:52,219
In the spring, I even went for a health examination.

552
00:34:52,219 --> 00:34:55,360
I checked my stomach and intestines, but there aren't any problems.

553
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:58,030
The doctor said I'm healthier

554
00:34:58,030 --> 00:35:00,440
than youngsters like you guys.

555
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:02,940
- Nothing is more important than health.
- That's great.

556
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:06,500
He is Xiao Hu, who used to live in your room.

557
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:08,520
Hello.

558
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:11,060
We'll head to the homestay first.

559
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:12,229
We won't bother you.

560
00:35:12,229 --> 00:35:14,199
Sure. I'll look for you guys tonight.

561
00:35:14,199 --> 00:35:16,250
Sure. You must come over.

562
00:35:16,250 --> 00:35:19,000
Take good care of that room.

563
00:35:20,780 --> 00:35:23,760
Why are you rubbing your soles? Is it dung?

564
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:26,260
That's good luck!

565
00:35:26,260 --> 00:35:29,450
I'll leave all of it here for you! All for you!

566
00:35:29,450 --> 00:35:31,640
- Let's go.
- Okay. See you tonight.

567
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:32,760
Okay. See you tonight.

568
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:35,809
Mr. Ma, there has been so much publicity for your store lately.

569
00:35:35,809 --> 00:35:37,220
