570
00:35:37,220 --> 00:35:38,880
Blind optimism is inadvisable.

571
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:43,929
Many tea stores have entered the market this year, but all of them were too similar.

572
00:35:43,929 --> 00:35:46,230
- The market has become extremely competitive.
- Competition is good.

573
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:47,720
That means there are prospects.

574
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:50,450
Everyone is diving into the market.

575
00:35:50,450 --> 00:35:53,189
Mr. Hu, what's going on with you and Sister Manjun?

576
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:56,030
