577
00:35:56,030 --> 00:36:00,629
- Da-ting? Dating? Still dating?
- Leave us be.

578
00:36:00,629 --> 00:36:02,320
What about you? Do you have a boyfriend now?

579
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,860
What do you mean? You're looking down on me, aren't you?

580
00:36:04,860 --> 00:36:06,109
Listen up.

581
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:09,040
I'm just uninterested. It's not that there aren't wooers. Got it?

582
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:11,880
I know. There was that guy called A'Hui, right?

583
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,280
That was like 800 years ago.

584
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:15,280
He even sent me a wedding invitation six months ago.

585
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:17,090
He might even have a baby now.

586
00:36:17,090 --> 00:36:19,230
Stop joking about that.

587
00:36:20,050 --> 00:36:21,929
Hongdou, where are your parents?

588
00:36:21,929 --> 00:36:24,480
They're playing Mahjong at Chairman Xie's place.

589
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:27,190
I'm going to pop the champagne!

590
00:36:30,070 --> 00:36:31,250
Here.

591
00:36:31,250 --> 00:36:32,500
Let me pour drinks for you guys.

592
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:35,469
Come on. Let's drink.

593
00:36:35,469 --> 00:36:36,560
Here you go.

594
00:36:36,560 --> 00:36:38,180
- Awesome.
- Here.

595
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:40,310
- Thank you.
- It's nothing.

596
00:36:41,130 --> 00:36:43,219
Are you guys ready?

597
00:36:43,219 --> 00:36:45,449
President Xu, say something!

598
00:36:45,449 --> 00:36:46,879
Applause!

599
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:49,270
- Everyone, applause!
- Give a speech!

600
00:36:49,270 --> 00:36:51,900
- A long one!
- All right.

601
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:56,160
Today is the soft opening of Gentle Breeze Homestay.

602
00:36:56,160 --> 00:36:59,699
I'd like to extend my sincere gratitude to my dear friends from all over the world

603
00:36:59,699 --> 00:37:06,019
