606
00:37:19,039 --> 00:37:21,520
I met all of you.

607
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:25,030
We had our own troubles.

608
00:37:25,780 --> 00:37:28,210
Fortunately, we've overcome those.

609
00:37:30,640 --> 00:37:33,020
Now that I'm meeting you again,

610
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:38,769
