611
00:37:40,130 --> 00:37:42,210
I truly feel happy for you.

612
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:47,000
Of course, I'm thankful for Chairman Xie.

613
00:37:48,490 --> 00:37:51,820
His Youfeng Courtyard gave us,

614
00:37:51,820 --> 00:37:54,060
